    <title>init_tag_manager()</title>
<indexterm><primary>init_tag_manager</primary><secondary>gestion_tag.h</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>gestion_tag.h</primary><secondary>init_tag_manager</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>void init_tag_manager (void )</computeroutput></para><para>

<para>Initialise/réinitialise le gestionnaire de tags. </para>
</para>

<para><note><title>Note</title>

<para>après sont appel, l&apos;ensemble des tags doivent être redéfinie avec l&apos;aide de <computeroutput><link linkend="_gestion__tag_8h_1a7301f247665ed1c0504f27602b3cf012">set_tag</link></computeroutput> </para>
</note>
</para>
